#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-oidc-auth0-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "xref:security-architecture.adoc[Quarkus Security] provides comprehensive OpenId Connect (OIDC) and OAuth2 support with its `quarkus-oidc` extension, supporting both xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc[Authorization code flow] and xref:security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc[Bearer token] authentication mechanisms."
msgstr "O xref:security-architecture.adoc[Quarkus Security] fornece suporte abrangente a OpenID Connect (OIDC) e OAuth2 com sua extensão `quarkus-oidc`, suportando os mecanismos de autenticação xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication.adoc[Authorization code flow] e xref:security-oidc-bearer-token-authentication.adoc[Bearer token]."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-oidc-auth0-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "With Quarkus, you can easily configure OIDC providers such as link:https://www.keycloak.org/documentation[Keycloak], link:https://developer.okta.com/[Okta], link:https://auth0.com/docs/[Auth0], and other xref:security-openid-connect-providers.adoc[well-known social OIDC and OAuth2 providers]."
msgstr "Com o Quarkus, você pode configurar facilmente provedores OIDC como link:https://www.keycloak.org/documentation[Keycloak], link:https://developer.okta.com/[Okta], link:https://auth0.com/docs/[Auth0] e outros xref:security-openid-connect-providers.adoc[provedores sociais OIDC e OAuth2 bem conhecidos]."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: gemini
#: _guides/security-oidc-auth0-tutorial.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Learn how to use the Quarkus OpenID Connect extension (`quarkus-oidc`) together with the https://auth0.com/docs/[Auth0] OIDC provider to protect your API endpoints."
msgstr "Aprenda como usar a extensão Quarkus OpenID Connect (`quarkus-oidc`) em conjunto com o provedor OIDC https://auth0.com/docs/[Auth0] para proteger seus endpoints de API."

